review:
I visited Excel dental care through my friends recommendation who was happy with the treatment result. Even I was surprised to see the incredible changes of before and after treatment.
So I decided that my braces treatment would be from Dr. JNANESHA H. C at Excel Dental Care *** ** *********** *** **** ************ ** ********** 
I had gaps between my teeth and my teeth was too front placed. It was embarrassing to speak and smile with irregularly placed teeth. 
I consulted Dr. Jnanesha and he explained about the treatment planning, cost, duration and types of braces.
I chose metal braces which was very affordable cost rs. 25k.the EMI payment option was very helpful and convenient.
During the treatment period I was comfortable and it was painless and booking appointment each month was convenient and easy. 
Dr. JNANESHA is available fulltime at excel dental  care, so appointment scheduling is very convenient.
The after treatment result is amazing. I now have perfectly aligned teeth and now I can speak and smile with confidence. 
I am very happy with Dr. Jnanesha 's orthodontic treatment and excel dental care dental clinic which is clean, big, hygienic, has all world class latest technology and easily accessible with ample parking space.
I highly recommend Dr. Jnanesha H. C and Excel Dental Care, Jayanagar ** *** **** ****** ****** for all your dental concern. Thank you.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I consulted Dr.Jnanesha for replacement of my missing teeth. Dr.Jnanesh and Dr.Sindhu explained various treatment plan ..... I chose to undergo permanent replacement of missing teeth so opted for Dental Implants. I was asked to get few blood tests and xrays done prior to the procedure. Since, I am a diabetic i was also asked to get my physician's consent. The procedure of fixing 2 implants were done in half an hour. I was comfortable during and after the procedure. After few weeks in was called for impression and template check in interval of few days. Then the teeth was fixed to the permanent implants. I am happy with the dental implants treatment by Dr.Jnanesh. 
I have got my tooth fillings, cleaning from Dr.Jnanesh . So being very happy with his work , I decided to get dental implants too from him.

I would highly recommend Dr.Jnanesh and excel dental care, Bangalore for all dental procedures. 
Thumbs up for clinic cleanliness ,sterilisation, clinic equipped with advanced dental technology, doctors experience and skill.
